dspace-development.title: Provide Support for HR Imports into Symplectic Elements for Digital Science

comments.body:
Attempting to synchronize this using the existing PowerShell tasks has yielded no results, and I must please recommend that the spreadsheets be reconciled. Currently, the HR feed provided from the Office of the Registrar is structured with the following columns:

![image.png](https://images.zenhubusercontent.com/5b5b6aed981c3204c9ed06c8/499dc7f4-00d5-4682-a534-c7060eda9947)

Please note that the HR feed provided by regularly-scheduled e-mail only contains records specifying students with theses prepared and submitted (hence, this will not satisfy the requirements for the new deployments).

https://princeton.service-now.com/now/workspace/agent/record/incident/bfd79ef21bf2b0d0ed5065b1604bcbf5 outlines the only viable approach which I would please propose as a feasible method for the new deployments.

1. Follow the steps here to create a new event: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FVzJkB4IxEQ
